  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Security Systems Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Job Highlights</p><ul><li>Good working environment with ongoing learning experience</li><li>Good Career Opportunity</li><li>Good Performance Incentives</li></ul><p>Job Description</p><p>Zectech is seeking motivated individuals to be responsible for project implementation of Security Systems in CCTV, Access Control, Intrusion Alarm and Wireless Networks.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities include</strong></p><ul><li>Planning, design, implementation and commissioning of security systems.</li><li>Provide remote as well as on-site technical support.</li><li>Perform regular system maintenance, upgrades, and troubleshooting to resolve any issues.</li><li>Prepare safety documents, checklist and reports related to system installations and maintenance.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Electrical and Electronic Engineering. Other Engineering courses may be consider.</li><li>At least 2 years of experience in the security systems industry. (Fresh graduates without any working experience are welcome to apply.)</li><li>Strong knowledge in security systems, computer networking and network topology.</li><li>Possesses a valid Class 3 driving licence is preferred.</li></ul><p>If you are resourceful, have a good working attitude and take pride in your work, send your resume to hr@zectech.com.sg. or visit our website at http://www.zectech.com.sg.</p>",
