    "description": "<h2>Specialist in Industrial Surveillance Solution</h2>\n<p><strong>Zectech Pte Ltd established in 2006 is a company providing a full-suite of solutions from A to Z in industrial surveillance. We have been growing rapidly in the Singapore market by providing state of the art and technologically advanced products and solutions in industries ranging from education to construction.</strong><br>\n<br>\n<strong>For the past 10 over years, we have dedicated ourselves towards ensuring satisfaction of our customers by meeting all their requirements and expectations. Through the years, we have deployed products and solutions featuring the latest technology, ideas and features such as AI, IOT, etc. to our customers premises and sites.</strong></p>",
